71
00:04:23,625 --> 00:04:24,416
Oh.

72
00:04:25,458 --> 00:04:26,708
Class Three, huh?

73
00:04:26,791 --> 00:04:28,416
That's Sena's Class.

74
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,041
You're in the student
council and ranked second

75
