76
00:04:31,333 --> 00:04:32,958
That's impressive.

77
00:04:33,041 --> 00:04:36,041
Your condescending attitude is
more than a little obnoxious!

78
00:04:36,125 --> 00:04:38,583
I don't need you to remind me
I've been Sena Kashiwazaki's

79
