chattin' her up left and right.

103
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:34,000
[KODAKA] This chick is not
what I'd call a listener.

104
00:05:34,083 --> 00:05:35,416
I mean, geez.

105
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:37,375
