her boyfriend as 'cool'.

110
00:05:47,625 --> 00:05:48,708
Are you talking about me?

111
00:05:48,791 --> 00:05:49,833
Uh.

112
00:05:49,916 --> 00:05:51,166
Do you see anyone
else standing there?

113
