to me like that before.

123
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:14,250
Why're you making
that stupid face?

124
00:06:14,333 --> 00:06:15,833
Come on!

125
00:06:15,916 --> 00:06:18,208
Great, so on top of being cool,
you also have a sense of humor!

126
00:06:18,291 --> 00:06:20,791
I can't help but be impressed,
but I hate it so much.

127
00:06:20,875 --> 00:06:22,833
Fine, you win; I'm
jealous of both of you!

128
00:06:22,916 --> 00:06:25,291
Mister Perfect and Little Miss
Perfect are perfect, perfect,

129
00:06:25,375 --> 00:06:26,708
perfect for each other!

130
00:06:26,791 --> 00:06:27,375
Vomit!

131
00:06:27,458 --> 00:06:28,500
