132
00:06:33,541 --> 00:06:36,166
[KODAKA]
So that's Aoi Yusa.

133
00:06:36,250 --> 00:06:39,416
Apparently this place is
freakin' packed with weirdos.

134
00:06:44,541 --> 00:06:45,000
Yo.

135
00:06:45,083 --> 00:06:46,541
What's up?

136
00:06:46,625 --> 00:06:47,416
[KODAKA]
Hey.

137
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:49,000
Why are you the only one here?

138
00:06:49,083 --> 00:06:52,083
Yozora and Rika left to go scout
out a new location for filming.

139
00:06:52,166 --> 00:06:54,833
Something about a shot of
the sun setting into the sea.

140
00:06:54,916 --> 00:06:56,125
Ah.

141
00:06:56,208 --> 00:06:57,291
Hey, on the way here.

142
00:06:57,375 --> 00:06:58,625
I ran into a girl

143
00:06:58,708 --> 00:07:00,666
named Aoi Yusa checking out
the finals rankings.

144
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:01,916
[SENA]
Who is that person?

145
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,708
[KODAKA] You mean you
don't already know her?

146
00:07:03,791 --> 00:07:04,958
She's in your class!

147
00:07:05,041 --> 00:07:05,750
[SENA]
What?

148
00:07:05,833 --> 00:07:07,125
She's kinda short

149
00:07:07,208 --> 00:07:09,291
and has this shortish
reddish hair thing going on?

150
00:07:09,375 --> 00:07:10,583
Oh yeah.

151
00:07:10,666 --> 00:07:12,833
Short and shortish
reddish kinda rings a bell.

152
00:07:12,916 --> 00:07:15,458
You should know the people
you're in class with, at least.

153
00:07:15,541 --> 00:07:16,625
Well, I memorized the names

154
00:07:16,708 --> 00:07:18,625
