157
00:07:22,125 --> 00:07:23,708
[SENA]
I told you.

158
00:07:23,791 --> 00:07:26,541
There are only two types
of girls in this world.

159
00:07:26,625 --> 00:07:27,833
Awesome girls.

160
00:07:27,916 --> 00:07:29,791
The kind I can be friends with.

161
00:07:29,875 --> 00:07:31,708
And all those other bitches.

162
00:07:31,791 --> 00:07:33,250
Besides.

163
00:07:33,333 --> 00:07:36,583
Why should I be forced to learn
a bunch of mongrels' names?

164
00:07:36,666 --> 00:07:38,875
[KODAKA] She calls the people
in her class mongrels?

165
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:41,791
Well, evidently this Aoi
girl isn't very happy that she's

166
00:07:41,875 --> 00:07:45,125
always listed right below you
on every single test ranking.

167
00:07:45,208 --> 00:07:47,583
