another students' rank?

168
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:50,125
Did you see the scores; where
are those things even posted?

169
00:07:50,208 --> 00:07:52,250
[KODAKA] On the bulletin
board in the courtyard!

170
00:07:52,333 --> 00:07:52,958
Oh.

171
00:07:53,041 --> 00:07:53,958
Guess that makes sense.

172
00:07:54,041 --> 00:07:55,541
[KODAKA]
You mean you never looked?

173
00:07:55,625 --> 00:07:57,875
[SENA] I don't have to; I can
tell my rank from the paper that

174
00:07:57,958 --> 00:08:00,000
has our percentiles
and stuff on it.

175
00:08:00,083 --> 00:08:02,541
The only thing that matters
to me is that I come in first.

176
00:08:02,625 --> 00:08:04,041
[KODAKA]
You really are something.

177
00:08:04,125 --> 00:08:05,583
Yeah, thank you.

178
00:08:05,666 --> 00:08:07,625
What kind of studying do you
normally do for your classes?

179
