183
00:08:13,041 --> 00:08:14,541
You study for tests,
though, right?

184
00:08:14,625 --> 00:08:17,083
Not besides that one time
we studied together.

185
00:08:17,166 --> 00:08:19,458
But hey, that was a pretty
good time, though, wasn't it?

186
00:08:19,541 --> 00:08:20,666
Oh, yeah.

187
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,166
Yeah, I guess it was.

188
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:24,208
[SENA]
So, what's the deal?

189
00:08:24,291 --> 00:08:26,750
Did something weird happen
with that Aoi girl?

190
00:08:26,833 --> 00:08:27,541
Meh.

191
00:08:27,625 --> 00:08:28,458
Never mind.

192
00:08:28,541 --> 00:08:29,916
Okay.

193
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,791
[KODAKA]
It's weird.

194
00:08:30,875 --> 00:08:32,125
She honestly couldn't care less

195
