what makes her happy

202
00:08:48,708 --> 00:08:50,750
and does exactly what she wants.

203
00:08:50,833 --> 00:08:52,916
It doesn't help that she's
got a crazy amount of talent

204
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:56,125
and a rich enough family
to get away with it all, too.

205
00:08:56,208 --> 00:08:58,208
