213
00:09:15,458 --> 00:09:16,458
[SENA]
Hey!

214
00:09:16,541 --> 00:09:17,750
[YOZORA] Why are
you still sitting?

215
00:09:17,833 --> 00:09:18,375
Let's go.

216
00:09:18,458 --> 00:09:19,000
[KODAKA]
Yeah.

217
00:09:19,083 --> 00:09:20,041
