235
00:09:59,833 --> 00:10:01,125
I wonder if she'll

236
00:10:01,208 --> 00:10:03,458
actually be able to make
that beach scene thing work.

237
00:10:03,541 --> 00:10:06,250
I mean, she's a scientist
not a CG expert.

238
00:10:06,333 --> 00:10:08,416
