244
00:10:17,166 --> 00:10:19,166
[PEGASUS] Our festival
atmosphere is rather pleasant,

245
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:20,541
don't you agree?

246
00:10:20,625 --> 00:10:21,083
[KODAKA]
Yeah.

247
00:10:21,166 --> 00:10:22,166
I guess it is.

248
00:10:27,708 --> 00:10:30,791
Now, if I recall correctly, your
club is doing a movie right?

249
00:10:30,875 --> 00:10:31,708
[KODAKA]
Yes, sir.

250
00:10:31,791 --> 00:10:33,708
I certainly enjoy a good flick.

251
00:10:33,791 --> 00:10:35,875
And believe it or not,
your father used to drag me out

252
00:10:35,958 --> 00:10:37,583
